init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The world is changing, and the people that remain must decide what to do with this new power.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The world is now full of possibilities, and with the right training, anything is possible.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: and we could use it to fight back against the aliens.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But if it does, we could have a chance at winning.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: but someone has to be, and it might as well be me.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: night after night, I'm ready, I'm going to do it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I'm scared, but I have to do this, I have to try.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I feel the energy flowing through me, I feel the power, I feel the magic.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: We can win this war, we can save the world.
